import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import axios from 'axios'; const FeedbackDetailsPage = ({ id }) => { const [feedback, setFeedback] = useState(null); const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true); const [error, setError] = useState(null); useEffect(() => { const fetchFeedback = async () => { try { const response = await axios.get(`http://localhost:3000/feedback`); // Ensure correct endpoint setFeedback(response.data); } catch (err) { setError(`Error fetching feedback details: ${err.message}`); // More informative error } finally { setLoading(false); } }; fetchFeedback(); }, [id]); if (loading) return
Loading...
; if (error) return
{error}
; if (!feedback) return
No feedback found
; return (

Feedback Details

Institution Name: {feedback.institutionName}
Website: {feedback.website}
Visit Date: {new Date(feedback.visitDate).toLocaleDateString()}
Staff Name: {feedback.staffName}
Staff Email: {feedback.staffEmail}
Staff Mobile: {feedback.staffMobile}
Total Students: {feedback.totalStudents}
Accompanying Staff: {feedback.accompanyingStaff}

Ratings

IPR Rating: {feedback.ratings ? feedback.ratings.iprRating : 'N/A'}
FCIPT Rating: {feedback.ratings ? feedback.ratings.fciptRating : 'N/A'}
Knowledge: {feedback.ratings ? feedback.ratings.knowledge : 'N/A'}
Explanations IPR: {feedback.ratings ? feedback.ratings.explanationsIPR : 'N/A'}
Explanations FCIPT: {feedback.ratings ? feedback.ratings.explanationsFCIPT : 'N/A'}
Knowledge Before: {feedback.ratings ? feedback.ratings.knowledgeBefore : 'N/A'}
Knowledge After: {feedback.ratings ? feedback.ratings.knowledgeAfter : 'N/A'}
Technical Contents: {feedback.ratings ? feedback.ratings.technicalContents : 'N/A'}
Ease of Understanding: {feedback.ratings ? feedback.ratings.easeOfUnderstanding : 'N/A'}

Additional Information

Sources: {feedback.sources.join(', ')}

Campuses: {feedback.campuses.join(', ')}

Best: {feedback.best}

Worst: {feedback.worst}

Suggestions: {feedback.suggestions}

Comments: {feedback.comments}

Created At: {new Date(feedback.createdAt).toLocaleString()}

Updated At: {new Date(feedback.updatedAt).toLocaleString()}

); }; export default FeedbackDetailsPage;
